the full suite run due to macOS Seatbelt restrictions on `.promptclaw/pets.json`, but `tests/test_sample_record_json.py` passed 100%.)\n\n## Verdict: PASS\n\n## Notes for Lead Agent\nThe JSON helpers are correctly wired. Note that `SampleLibrary` (SQLite) still uses its own mapping logic and does not yet persist the newly added analysis/context fields; if these fields are required in the SQL index, the schema and mapping will need a separate update. The hardening items regarding `bootstrap_identity` were considered out of scope for this data-structure utility task.\n"}}
